text: Sparta Township is a township in Sussex County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 United States Census, the population was 19,600.Table 7. Population for the Counties and Municipalities in New Jersey: 1990, 2000 and 2010, New Jersey Department of Labor and Workforce Development, February 2011.
